  "title": "🦅 Events Role – No Boring Desk Job 🚫🪑 (Real Career Growth!)",
  "description": "<p>We’re an outsourced sales and marketing team partnering with reputable brands across industries — telco, broadband, lifestyle products, even charity causes. Our job? Bring brands to life by engaging customers directly — anywhere, anytime.</p><p>This is a <strong>consumer-focused role</strong>, which means you’ll work with a <strong>larger market and bigger crowd</strong>. The more people you meet, the more impact and results you create.</p><p>If you enjoy creating conversations, connecting with people, and working with a fun, motivated team, this role will be a great fit.</p><h3><strong>Your Mission</strong></h3><ul><li>Engage customers face-to-face and share about brand campaigns</li><li>Create a positive experience and build trust</li><li>Guide customers to solutions that fit their needs</li><li>Work with a high-energy team while achieving targets together</li></ul><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li>Energetic, outgoing, and curious</li><li>Enjoys meeting new people</li><li>No experience needed — full training provided</li></ul><h3><strong>Why You’ll Love It</strong></h3><ul><li>Good commission & incentive structure</li><li>Fast progression for high performers</li><li>Build confidence, communication, and presentation skills</li><li>Supportive, youthful team environment</li></ul>",
